headline: Zeta, Teladoc, Jamf, Dayforce, and 8x8 Shares Are Falling, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the afternoon session after a broader market sell-off triggered by renewed trade tensions. U.S. stock indices fell after the Trump administration announced intentions to impose a 35% tariff on many goods imported from Canada.
